caption.body: Filmmaker Nicole Teeny celebrates one of the world’s first Queer-affirming and gender-equal mosques, located in Toronto and co-founded by Imam El-Farouk and his husband Troy.   See “Unity Mosque” by Nicole Teeny in the Video Arts Gallery, located pre-security in the International Terminal with daily operating hours of 7:00am to 10:00pm, or online at: https://bit.ly/3tb#lgbt   Director & Producer: Nicole Teeny @nicoleteeny Producer: Jordan Ehrlich @cavelightfilms Sound: Bridget Tang @sonicbarista  DP: Issa Shah @issashahdp AP: Mariel Sarkis @marielsarkis Editor: Mike Feldman @feldmikeman  PA: Hamzah Amin @hamzahamin
